<title>SINGAPORE: HWGI unit lands 5.0 mln ringgit overdraft.</title>
<headline>HWGI unit lands 5.0 mln ringgit overdraft.</headline>
<dateline>SINGAPORE 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Precision engineering service firm Ho Wah Genting International Ltd (HWGI) said on Thursday it had concluded a 5.0 million ringgit overdraft credit package for its Malaysian unit, Ho Wah Genting Electric Sdn Bhd (HWGE).</p>
<p>The funds would be used for working capital, HWGI said in a statement.</p>
<p>The overdraft has been secured on HWGE's factory, plant and machinery, equipment and furniture and fittings it recently acquired in Malacca. It is also backed by a corporate guarantee.</p>
<p>-- Singapore newsroom (65 8703011)</p>
